Hey there, [Parallax Wave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Wave) and [Parallax Tide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Tide)! I heard you like to leave the battlefield at instant speed.  

@Donovan\_Fabian:  
Unfortunately, [Rancor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor) can't be replayed on your opponent's turn. You'd need something like [Vedalken Orrery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vedalken Orrery) to pull it off effectively. Plus, that would require a four-color deck. Maybe [Brilliant Halo](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brilliant Halo), [Despondency](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Despondency), [Launch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Launch), or [Spirit Loop](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit Loop) would be easier.

